data.description: Charming home in Pueblo is waiting for you. The large front porch is welcoming and a great place to relax. Upon entering the home, you will notice the special touches this home has, such as the trim work and arched wall between the living room and dining room. Cozy up in the living room in front of the wood burning fireplace. The living room has built-in cabinets that surround the fireplace. The main floor has the kitchen, a mudroom with access to the covered back patio and fenced backyard. You will also find 2 bedrooms and the full bath on the main level. The basement has an additional bedroom, laundry room, and space to add your finishing touches. There is access to the one car attached garage from the basement. Outside you will find an additional one car garage/storage shed.
